50|$|The Wines of Alsace by Tom Stevenson was {{published}} in 1993 by Faber & Faber. This 600 page book profiles 300 producers, 118 <b>wine</b> <b>villages,</b> 51 grands crus, 84 lieux-dits, 28 clos and 4 wine-producing châteaux of Alsace. The vintage chart stretches from 1992 back to 585.|$|R
